{recipeDescription}             --- The description of the a recipe. ---
{difficultySelect}              --- Consists of a component that display and selects the difficulty of a recipe. ---
{recipeThumbnail}               --- Selects the Thumbnail image of a recipe ---
{requiredRecipeTime}            --- Selects the required time to prepare a single recipe ---
{recipeTitle}                   --- Selects the name or title of a single recipe ---
{recipePage}                    --- Selects the page of the displayed recipe ---

{requiredPhpDifficultySelect}   --- Required Php to diplay the correct difficulty for a recipe ---